3:T89b,<p>The cypress leaf necklace is a stunning gold plated sterling silver pendant designed to bring the beauty of nature into your everyday style. This nature inspired gift features a delicate vein design that captures the unique shape and intricate details of a real cypress leaf, symbolizing hope, immortality, and elevation. Handmade with care from recycled silver jewelry, this artisan crafted necklace blends sustainable jewelry gift practices with timeless elegance.</p>
<p>- Crafted from recycled sterling silver 925 and finished with durable gold plating that resists tarnish for lasting shine<br />
- Features a delicate vein design preserving the natural beauty of the cypress leaf in every leaf pendant necklace<br />
- Measures perfectly to fit comfortably as a pendant necklace, ideal for layering or wearing solo<br />
- Handmade gold necklace created using rare techniques perfected over years to merge nature art necklace qualities with wearable jewelry<br />
- Eco friendly jewelry made sustainably since 2011 in Athens by MNJRealFlowerJewelry<br />
- Each piece arrives beautifully gift boxed, ready as a nature inspired gift for loved ones or special keepsakes<br />
- Free worldwide shipping available; contact us for exclusive distributors in your area<br />
- Mother Nature Jewellery donates 1 € from every sale to Lalibela, supporting children in need through education and care</p>
<p>This symbolic leaf jewelry is more than just an accessory—it is a meaningful statement of sustainability and artistry. The polished gold plated necklace offers both elegance and durability, while the recycled silver pendant supports eco friendly jewelry values. Wearing this cypress leaf necklace connects you to nature’s timeless inspiration and contributes to positive change.</p>
<p>Choose this sustainable jewelry gift to enjoy a handmade gold necklace that honors the environment and craftsmanship. Its unique design makes it perfect for those who appreciate delicate vein design details and artisan crafted necklaces. Whether for yourself or as a thoughtful nature inspired gift, this cypress leaf necklace combines beauty, symbolism, and eco-consciousness in one exquisite piece.</p>
4:T997,<p>Silver twig earrings bring the enchanting beauty of nature to your everyday style with these handmade sterling silver statement branch jewelry pieces. Designed to capture organic charm, these silver twig earrings offer lovers of nature inspired jewelry a unique way to express elegance and individuality. Crafted from recycled silver jewelry materials, each pair features mismatched silver earrings that showcase the delicate veins of real pine branches, combining artistry with eco friendly earrings benefits.</p>
<p>These large twig earrings are artisan crafted earrings made using a rare technique developed over years to coat real plants in precious metals. The natural twig jewelry is sealed with a tarnish-resistant varnish that ensures lasting shine and durability. Each pair is a statement branch earrings design, perfect for both special occasions and everyday wear, offering unmatched uniqueness due to natural variations in the original plant material.</p>
<p>- Handmade sterling silver 925 with silver and gold plating highlights every detail of pine branch earrings<br />
- Mismatched design creates bold, large twig earrings that stand out as unique nature earrings<br />
- Eco friendly earrings made from recycled silver jewelry support sustainable fashion<br />
- Tarnish-resistant varnish maintains shine and protects organic charm earrings over time<br />
- Each pair is artisan crafted earrings using nature inspired jewelry molds for authenticity<br />
- Handmade in Athens since 2011 by MNJRealFlowerJewelry, trusted for quality and creativity<br />
- Arrives beautifully gift boxed for easy gifting or personal treat</p>
<p>Mother Nature Jewellery donates 1 € from every sale to Lalibela, supporting children in need worldwide. This commitment adds meaningful value to your purchase of these unique nature earrings. Whether you seek statement branch earrings or organic charm earrings, these mismatched silver earrings blend craftsmanship and sustainability seamlessly.</p>
<p>Experience the magic of natural twig jewelry that celebrates the artistry of the environment while offering you timeless style. With every detail carefully preserved through expert artisan crafting techniques, these eco friendly earrings embody a perfect balance between beauty and responsibility. Choose silver twig earrings that tell a story, support sustainability, and elevate your jewelry collection with pieces that are truly one-of-a-kind.</p>
5:T5b6,<p>Discover the elegance of nature captured in this exquisite gold mimosa ring, a perfect statement ring that celebrates the delicate beauty of the mimosa leaf. Crafted as a solid gold ring available in 9K, 14K, or 18K yellow, white, or rose gold, this piece blends organic inspiration with timeless design. Whether you're drawn to bridal jewelry or simply want a unique accessory, this real plant ring brings a touch of the outdoors to your everyday style.</p>
<p>- Crafted from a real Acacia leaf, symbolizing renewal, fortitude, and purity<br />
- Available in 9K, 14K, or 18K solid gold; choose yellow, white, or rose gold at no extra cost<br />
- Wide band design offers comfortable wear and a bold presence<br />
- Handmade using a rare technique that coats natural leaves in recycled solid gold<br />
- Each ring is made to order with a processing time of 3-4 days</p>
<p>All rings arrive beautifully gift boxed for easy gifting.</p>
<p>- Select your preferred gold karat and color by specifying in your order notes or messaging directly<br />
- Please note: yellow gold hue varies slightly between 9K, 14K, and 18K options</p>
<p>Mother Nature Jewellery has been bringing art and nature together since 2011 from Athens. Using a unique process perfected over years, each piece reflects the artist’s passion for nature and craftsmanship. Follow us on Facebook at , we donate €1 to Lalibela to help save children's lives through education and care.</p>
6:T839,<p>Gold hoop earrings crafted with 14k gold plated hoops and real leaf botanical design offer a nature-inspired elegance perfect for everyday wear or special occasions. These gold hoop earrings combine eco friendly earrings style with sustainable materials, featuring real Araucaria leaves preserved within each piece to highlight their delicate vein details. Handmade jewelry lovers will appreciate the blend of artistry and environmental care in these sterling silver hoops, designed to bring a unique bohemian style earrings look that complements any outfit.</p>
<p>- Made from recycled silver jewelry sterling silver 925 with durable 14k gold plating for lasting shine and hypoallergenic comfort<br />
- Features authentic real leaf earrings crafted using molds from actual Araucaria leaves to capture intricate botanical details<br />
- Secure butterfly clip closure ensures comfortable, reliable wear throughout the day<br />
- Mini hoop earrings sized perfectly for subtle yet eye-catching style<br />
- Arrives beautifully gift boxed, making an ideal gift for mom or anyone who loves nature inspired jewelry</p>
<p>Each pair of these handmade jewelry pieces is carefully crafted by skilled artisans using rare techniques that transform real flowers and plants into wearable art. The recycled silver jewelry base supports sustainability without compromising quality or beauty. These 14k gold plated hoops coordinate perfectly with matching Araucaria rings and necklaces available in our collection, allowing you to create a cohesive nature-inspired look.</p>
<p>Mother Nature Jewelry donates 1 € from every sale to Lalibela, supporting children in need, adding a meaningful impact to your purchase. Please allow processing time for this handcrafted item before shipping. For questions or custom requests, feel free to contact us at info [!at] ’s beauty at our  store.</p>
<p>Experience the perfect combination of botanical earrings charm and sustainable craftsmanship with these gold hoop earrings that bring natural elegance and bohemian style earrings flair into your jewelry collection.</p>
7:T67b,<div class="info-content">
<p>Handcrafted by women artisans, these bags are made of hand-embroidered cotton fabric which is very durable. Designed to keep your yoga essentials neatly organized with a spacious interior and zippered pockets, each bags is fully lined with solid cotton fabric that gives extra strength to hold heavy mats. The bag comes with a wide adjustable shoulder strap to hold the mats comfortably.</p>
<p> <span>We believe passionately that fashion and function shouldn’t have to be sacrificed for each other. We aim to fill the needs of yoga practitioners who love fashion and style but still need to carry yoga mats and organize their stuff in a functional way. For organizing the small stuff there </span>is<span> inner and outer zippered pockets. The bag comes with a wide adjustable shoulder strap to hold the mats comfortably.</span></p>
<p> </p>
<p>Made in India.</p>
</div>
<div class="">
<div id="productDetail-details">
<div class="info-content">
<div>
<p>Details: Cotton canvas. Drawstring closure. One interior zip pocket, 2 exterior zip pockets.</p>
<p> </p>
</div>
