<div>
<span class="details-label">Product Dimensions:</span><span class="dimension-value">H 29.0 Centimeters</span><span> </span><span>x</span><span> </span><span class="dimension-value">W 7.5 Centimeters</span><span> </span><span>x</span><span> </span><span class="dimension-value">L 11.0 Centimeters</span>
</div>
</li>
